[Adapted from Mo Shu Bai's novel,
The Princess Royal on jjwxc.net]

3
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

4
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 18]

5
00:01:39,820 --> 00:01:40,580
Your Highness!

6
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:42,620
Your Highness!

7
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:44,980
The Prince Consort is back.

8
00:01:46,620 --> 00:01:49,660
♪In the shower of petals♪

9
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:52,900
What did you say?

10
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:55,300
What did you just say?

11
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:57,980
♪And the stars twinkle. At this moment♪

12
00:01:57,980 --> 00:02:00,780
Did you say Pei Wenxuan is back?

13
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:02,220
Really?

14
00:02:02,380 --> 00:02:05,020
The Prince Consort... The Prince Consort
is back in the capital.

15
00:02:05,020 --> 00:02:06,860
♪It's hard to tell
what's right or wrong♪

16
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:09,820
♪I forgot to lock both our memories♪

17
00:02:09,820 --> 00:02:12,300
♪Pupils are enchanted♪

18
00:02:12,940 --> 00:02:15,340
Quickly. Ask someone to find out more

19
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,780
and keep me posted.

20
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:19,100
Besides,

21
00:02:20,340 --> 00:02:21,700
send people
to guard the imperial hall at once.

22
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:22,950
As soon as there's news
from the imperial hall

23
00:02:22,950 --> 00:02:23,940
that the Qin Family
has been pardoned,

24
00:02:23,940 --> 00:02:25,250
have all the men
of the Inspectorate Office

25
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:26,140
clear the royal path

26
00:02:26,380 --> 00:02:27,420
to ensure
that the Imperial Decree Bearer

27
00:02:27,420 --> 00:02:29,100
can arrive
at the execution site unimpeded.

28
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:29,660
Yes.

29
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,340
Go now.

30
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:31,340
I'll go right away.

31
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:32,500
♪To take the risk, to make the decision♪

32
00:02:32,500 --> 00:02:36,900
♪To break through♪

33
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:42,700
♪In the shower of petals,
and the stars twinkle♪

34
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:48,420
♪Make the decision
to love you to the moon and back♪

35
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:54,980
♪Don't be afraid of changes,
there's no escaping destiny♪

36
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:57,540
♪The dream
from the previous life is fading♪

37
00:02:57,540 --> 00:02:58,220
Mr. Su.

38
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:01,260
Pei Wenxuan...

39
00:03:03,060 --> 00:03:03,740
is back.

40
00:03:04,380 --> 00:03:05,460
I heard that.

41
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:09,940
What you just said...

42
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:11,420
Please forget...

43
00:03:13,540 --> 00:03:15,580
about what I said, Your Highness.

44
00:03:17,860 --> 00:03:19,060
Don't take it to heart.

45
00:03:28,460 --> 00:03:29,260
Mr. Xie.

46
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:31,380
Why are you here?

47
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:41,660
But I haven't received
an imperial order from His Majesty.

48
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:43,580
My master said he'd be responsible
for any problems caused.

49
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:44,700
Execute them first.

50
00:03:54,670 --> 00:03:55,120
[Execute]

51
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,120
[Beibang Inn]

52
00:04:07,980 --> 00:04:09,020
It's time.

53
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:16,180
Execute!

54
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:19,540
Let's take action.

55
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:33,690
The time is not yet up

56
00:04:33,690 --> 00:04:35,180
and the imperial decree
hasn't yet arrived.

57
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:36,860
How could you execute them beforehand?

58
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:38,300
How dare you!

59
00:04:38,300 --> 00:04:40,660
You are now in the capital,
the imperial city.

60
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,660
How dare you openly rescue criminals

61
00:04:42,780 --> 00:04:43,980
disregarding the law?

62
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,220
Arrest them!

63
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:53,700
Halt the execution!

64
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:58,380
His Majesty has ordered
to halt the execution.

65
00:05:02,940 --> 00:05:04,660
Here's the evidence I've obtained.

66
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:05,900
Your Majesty, please take a look at it.

67
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:15,180
Your Majesty, what you see here

68
00:05:15,340 --> 00:05:17,660
are the records I transcribed
of the provisions and funds in transit

69
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:18,580
from the county offices

70
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:20,860
along the way that I visited.

71
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:24,300
Go ahead.

72
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:27,340
In addition to these records,

73
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:30,660
I've also
asked the local soldiers and people

74
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:32,780
to record their testimonies of the war.

75
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:34,060
In that war,
half the soldiers had suffered

76
00:05:34,420 --> 00:05:36,540
from starvation and illness
before the war started.

77
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:37,650
[A soldier defending Huangping County]
They couldn't fight

78
00:05:37,650 --> 00:05:38,820
without enough to eat.

79
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:40,660
But under this circumstance,

80
00:05:41,060 --> 00:05:44,260
the Qin Family was still able
to safely evacuate the people in advance

81
00:05:44,380 --> 00:05:45,780
without causing too many casualties.

82
00:05:46,260 --> 00:05:47,340
[A soldier in battle]
In my opinion,

83
00:05:47,500 --> 00:05:48,580
the Qin Family

84
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,780
should not be punished.

85
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:50,860
Instead, they should be rewarded.

86
00:05:51,140 --> 00:05:51,860
Your Majesty,

87
00:05:52,220 --> 00:05:54,140
don't ever disappoint the soldiers
at the border.

88
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,140
Pei Wenxuan,

89
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:58,660
do you have any idea
what your words mean?

90
00:06:03,420 --> 00:06:04,860
Your Majesty,
I implore you to thoroughly investigate

91
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:07,040
the embezzlement
of military provisions and funds

92
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,340
by the counties in Huangping County.

93
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:10,940
It's a false accusation.

94
00:06:11,100 --> 00:06:14,060
Your Majesty,
he's making a false accusation.

95
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:17,180
Pei Wenxuan, do you know

96
00:06:17,180 --> 00:06:18,580
how many officials in the Great Xia

97
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:20,260
will be wronged, humiliated

98
00:06:20,260 --> 00:06:23,260
and implicated if you make

99
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,660
such a casual remark?

100
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,820
If it's a false accusation,
it'll be found out.

101
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:29,700
Your Majesty,
I implore you to thoroughly investigate

102
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:31,700
the Ministry of Justice,
the Ministry of Revenue,

103
00:06:31,820 --> 00:06:33,260
the Ministry of War, and the Censorate

104
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:34,900
to clear the Qin Family's name

105
00:06:35,180 --> 00:06:36,780
and bring justice
to the soldiers at the border.

106
00:06:36,780 --> 00:06:38,780
Pei Wenxuan, what do you mean?

107
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:40,980
The Ministry of Justice, War,
Revenue, and the Censorate?

108
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,860
Are you saying
that everyone in the imperial court

109
00:06:42,860 --> 00:06:44,500
is working together to hide the truth
and frame the Qin Family?

110
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:46,580
Is it worth it for a mere Qin Family?

111
00:06:47,060 --> 00:06:49,260
Besides, as an investigating censor,

112
00:06:49,260 --> 00:06:50,100
you were not doing your job,

113
00:06:50,100 --> 00:06:51,740
yet you deceived His Majesty
and left the capital without permission.

114
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:52,350
When you're back,

115
00:06:52,350 --> 00:06:54,220
you've fabricated a bunch of evidence
to deceive His Majesty.

116
00:06:54,380 --> 00:06:56,860
Do you think His Majesty
can be fooled by you?

117
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:57,900
You checked the accounts.

118
00:06:58,420 --> 00:07:00,340
What kind of authority do you have

119
00:07:01,100 --> 00:07:02,580
as an investigating censor

120
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:05,420
that allows you
to check so many existing accounts?

121
00:07:05,460 --> 00:07:06,740
Why would they give you those accounts?

122
00:07:08,140 --> 00:07:10,540
How did you exactly get those accounts?

123
00:07:15,460 --> 00:07:17,100
Your Majesty,
I implore you to look into this.

124
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:17,840
- Your Majesty,
- Your Majesty,

125
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:19,100
- I implore you to look into this.
- I implore you to look into this.

126
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:20,740
Your Majesty,
I implore you to look into this.

127
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:21,710
- Your Majesty,
- Your Majesty,

128
00:07:21,710 --> 00:07:22,700
- I implore you to look into this.
- I implore you to look into this.

129
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:23,900
Your Majesty,
I implore you to look into this.

130
00:07:25,540 --> 00:07:28,020
Your Majesty, the soldiers at the border

131
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:29,700
are not only guarding the border,

132
00:07:30,060 --> 00:07:31,660
but also the land and the people

133
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,660
of the Great Xia.

134
00:07:42,500 --> 00:07:45,020
Pei Wenxuan, you've had a long journey.

135
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:47,220
This case is very important

136
00:07:48,260 --> 00:07:49,460
and involves a lot of people.

137
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:52,140
Let me think about it.

138
00:07:52,780 --> 00:07:53,620
You must be tired.

139
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,300
You can leave now and get some rest.

140
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:55,780
Your Majesty...

141
00:07:55,780 --> 00:07:58,060
What? Didn't I make myself clear?

142
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:08,740
Yes, Your Majesty.

143
00:08:08,740 --> 00:08:09,420
Wait.

144
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:13,940
Now, Pingyue is grounded
at Beiyan Pagoda.

145
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:15,420
Go and pick her up.

146
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:17,100
You can go home together.

147
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:19,420
Yes, Your Majesty.

148
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,940
Your Highness,
working with the noble families

149
00:08:23,460 --> 00:08:24,780
to help the Crown Prince
ascend the throne

150
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:27,100
is the best path for you.

151
00:08:27,860 --> 00:08:29,460
If the Inspectorate Office
is to be established,

152
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:31,860
you still need
to have a sense of proportion.

153
00:08:33,260 --> 00:08:35,380
Power struggles involve strife.

154
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,740
Please be careful, Your Highness.

155
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:55,260
I don't want to be
your enemy, Your Highness.

156
00:08:58,260 --> 00:09:00,140
I just hope you can lead a good life.

157
00:09:04,620 --> 00:09:05,540
I've lost...

158
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,580
this one.

159
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,620
Your Highness, you must have
a lot of things to attend to.

160
00:09:16,260 --> 00:09:18,340
I'll take my leave now.

161
00:09:24,060 --> 00:09:24,900
Su Rongqing.

162
00:09:28,100 --> 00:09:29,500
Are you also...?

163
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,060
Nothing.

164
00:09:45,900 --> 00:09:46,620
See you.

165
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:14,100
You didn't attend today's morning court,

166
00:10:15,140 --> 00:10:16,940
but you've come
to Beiyan Pagoda for a stroll.

167
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:18,580
It seems like you're in a good mood.

168
00:10:19,060 --> 00:10:20,500
I came to see Her Highness
for something.

169
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:24,460
It seems to be something urgent.

170
00:10:27,580 --> 00:10:28,580
Mr. Pei,

171
00:10:29,940 --> 00:10:32,340
you are afraid of me
meeting Her Highness, aren't you?

172
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:35,820
It's broad daylight.

173
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,460
What nonsense are you talking about?

174
00:10:38,380 --> 00:10:40,060
Why am I afraid
of you meeting Her Highness?

175
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:44,580
You asked me

176
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:47,220
to be your groomsman to fetch
Her Highness on your wedding day.

177
00:10:47,940 --> 00:10:49,940
You intended to curry favor
with Her Highness.

178
00:10:50,860 --> 00:10:51,980
But then you found out

179
00:10:52,660 --> 00:10:53,940
that she liked me.

180
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:55,580
Right?

181
00:11:00,020 --> 00:11:00,900
So what?

182
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:04,060
I'm the one

183
00:11:04,820 --> 00:11:05,860
who's with Her Highness now.

184
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:12,260
Pei Wenxuan.

185
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:15,780
How can feel at ease

186
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:17,420
when you say things like that?

187
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:20,580
Don't forget

188
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:22,980
that if it wasn't for His Majesty's
fear of the imperial relatives,

189
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,420
you wouldn't have even been able

190
00:11:24,540 --> 00:11:26,260
to get close to Her Highness
in your life.

191
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,780
Not to mention

192
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:30,940
to be with Her Highness.

193
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:38,060
Let me remind you of something, too.

194
00:11:39,420 --> 00:11:41,580
If you miss it, you miss it.

195
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:45,900
Since I'm with Her Highness now,

196
00:11:46,740 --> 00:11:49,260
I won't give her up to anyone else.

197
00:11:49,580 --> 00:11:52,100
No matter whether it's in the past
or the future,

198
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:56,620
you won't get another chance.

199
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,220
Aren't you curious

200
00:12:10,180 --> 00:12:11,740
about what I told Her Highness?

201
00:12:13,260 --> 00:12:14,500
I told Her Highness...

202
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:19,580
that I'd like to marry her.

203
00:12:30,580 --> 00:12:32,500
Unfortunately, you're back.

204
00:12:34,820 --> 00:12:35,660
Pei Wenxuan.

205
00:12:37,220 --> 00:12:39,100
I don't know why you are so confident.

206
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:43,380
You think that you can
totally own Her Highness from now on?

207
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:47,500
But the way to protect Her Highness

208
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:48,940
is not to ask her

209
00:12:49,140 --> 00:12:50,940
to against everyone
in the imperial court with you

210
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:52,500
or to make her take

211
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:54,020
on the burden
of inspecting all the officials.

212
00:12:54,900 --> 00:12:55,860
If you ever put Her Highness

213
00:12:55,980 --> 00:12:58,420
in this kind of danger
in the future again,

214
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:00,700
then remember...

215
00:13:02,620 --> 00:13:04,060
you will forever

216
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,900
lose Her Highness.

217
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:10,460
Pei Wenxuan.

218
00:13:12,380 --> 00:13:14,500
You won't always be so lucky.

219
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:22,220
Su Rongqing, listen here.

220
00:13:24,260 --> 00:13:25,860
You are no one to judge

221
00:13:26,180 --> 00:13:27,900
how I treat Her Highness.

222
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:30,780
Besides,

223
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:34,140
I don't care what you say
to Her Highness

224
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:36,540
because I know

225
00:13:37,020 --> 00:13:38,660
Her Highness won't say yes to you.

226
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:45,580
Whether Her Highness agrees or not

227
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:49,740
is something you should find out
for yourself.

228
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:55,420
I'll still say the same thing.

229
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:05,140
Don't let Her Highness down.

230
00:14:06,740 --> 00:14:07,780
Conduct yourself well.

231
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:25,940
Your Highness!

232
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:28,300
The Prince Consort...

233
00:14:28,860 --> 00:14:30,340
The Prince Consort is at the foot
of the pagoda.

234
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:37,940
[Beiyan Pagoda]

235
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:38,740
Your Highness!

236
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,820
Your Highness, slowly.

237
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:42,260
Be careful.

238
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:07,300
You're back.

239
00:15:08,660 --> 00:15:09,500
Pei Wenxuan.

240
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:19,420
Rong.

241
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:22,300
I'm here to take you home.

242
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,300
Well...

243
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:14,420
We haven't seen each other in a while
so I've forgot myself.

244
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:16,900
If I've offended you in any way...

245
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:17,660
Does it hurt?

246
00:16:19,660 --> 00:16:20,260
Your injuries.

247
00:16:24,060 --> 00:16:24,900
Yes, it does.

248
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:28,500
It hurts everywhere.

249
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:43,660
Mr. Tian, you'd better confess.

250
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:48,180
The Prince Consort is already back.

251
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:50,820
The evidence he obtained is enough
to put a lot of people at risk.

252
00:16:51,060 --> 00:16:52,500
Why don't you keep yourself safe first?

253
00:16:52,500 --> 00:16:53,900
Trying to trick me
into talking about it?

254
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,060
You're too young for that.

255
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,140
If you're like this,

256
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,060
I'll write a memorial

257
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:03,500
about you

258
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:05,300
and submit it to the Censorate.

259
00:17:05,580 --> 00:17:06,340
Mr. Tian,

260
00:17:06,780 --> 00:17:08,460
think about it carefully.

261
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:10,060
Wait.

262
00:17:11,980 --> 00:17:14,740
Recently, Tian Zhong and the others
have disappeared one after another.

263
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:16,220
The situation is not encouraging.

264
00:17:16,780 --> 00:17:18,820
I'm afraid
they've got something on them.

265
00:17:19,140 --> 00:17:19,980
All these people

266
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:22,300
have been reported by the Censorate,
right?

267
00:17:24,460 --> 00:17:25,500
What are you

268
00:17:25,780 --> 00:17:27,380
going to do about them, Mr. Shangguan?

269
00:17:28,300 --> 00:17:31,260
They've been warned to be careful
with their words and actions,

270
00:17:31,420 --> 00:17:32,420
but they just won't listen.

