Mr. Su,

548
00:33:32,300 --> 00:33:33,340
As the Prince Consort,

549
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:34,900
what's wrong with me

550
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:36,060
standing next to Her Highness?

551
00:33:39,820 --> 00:33:42,060
Enter the hall!

552
00:33:43,580 --> 00:33:44,220
Pingyue,

553
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:47,500
how's the case I asked you
to investigate going?

554
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:48,820
Father,

555
00:33:48,860 --> 00:33:51,060
the Qin Family's case
is basically cleared up.

556
00:33:54,460 --> 00:33:56,100
The case originated
from the Ministry of War.

557
00:33:56,100 --> 00:33:58,100
The Ministry of War failed
to keep the Military Record,

558
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,660
resulting in missing pages
in the record.

559
00:33:59,820 --> 00:34:01,420
An official noticed

560
00:34:01,420 --> 00:34:03,380
that the battle
in Huangping County was unusual

561
00:34:03,580 --> 00:34:05,020
and blurted it out.

562
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:06,860
[The Qin Family's case originated]
Then, a kind man went to Mr. Wen Ping

563
00:34:06,860 --> 00:34:09,740
[from the Ministry of War]
and reported the Qin Family.

564
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:12,740
So Mr. Wen worked with Mr. Cui Shuyun
of the Ministry of Justice

565
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:13,740
to investigate the case.

566
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:16,780
But they neglected their duties
in the course of investigating the case,

567
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:19,260
resulting in a wrongful conviction.

568
00:34:19,420 --> 00:34:21,340
Now that the Qin Family's name
has been cleared,

569
00:34:21,700 --> 00:34:23,390
I hope that you can severely punish
Wang Xi,

570
00:34:23,390 --> 00:34:24,980
the Bureau Director
of the Ministry of War,

571
00:34:25,220 --> 00:34:26,820
Wen Ping of the Censorate,

572
00:34:27,100 --> 00:34:28,700
Cui Shuyun of the Ministry of Justice,

573
00:34:28,820 --> 00:34:30,740
and the others involved in the case.

574
00:34:31,220 --> 00:34:32,300
In addition to the Qin Family's case,

575
00:34:32,300 --> 00:34:34,420
I've also sorted out the embezzlement
of military provisions and funds

576
00:34:34,420 --> 00:34:36,220
related to this case.

577
00:34:36,220 --> 00:34:38,580
I've also provided a list
of the names of those involved.

578
00:34:38,820 --> 00:34:41,740
I implore you to allow me to conduct
a thorough investigation, Father.

579
00:34:42,700 --> 00:34:43,540
Well done.

580
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:47,220
Look.

581
00:34:48,620 --> 00:34:51,220
When I first wanted
to establish the Inspectorate Office,

582
00:34:51,220 --> 00:34:52,540
you stopped me.

583
