You said Pingyue was too young
to do anything.

584
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:58,340
So, how's the case going?

585
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:01,940
I think it's going very well.

586
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:04,340
It's been investigated clearly

587
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:06,060
and there's not a single mistake.

588
00:35:06,340 --> 00:35:07,460
If it weren't for Pingyue,

589
00:35:08,460 --> 00:35:10,420
I wouldn't know that you officials

590
00:35:11,220 --> 00:35:13,460
were so capable.

591
00:35:17,620 --> 00:35:20,300
Your Majesty, I think

592
00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:22,300
it's fortunate that by the grace of God,

593
00:35:23,740 --> 00:35:26,700
Her Highness is able
to supervise the officials

594
00:35:26,740 --> 00:35:28,300
with great success.

595
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:31,700
The Shangguan Family has begun
an internal investigation,

596
00:35:31,700 --> 00:35:34,460
and we'll get rid

597
00:35:34,820 --> 00:35:36,340
of all those involved.

598
00:35:36,730 --> 00:35:37,810
These evil actions are not

599
00:35:37,820 --> 00:35:40,540
what the Shangguan Family wants,

600
00:35:40,660 --> 00:35:44,100
even if it's just one man's corruption.

601
00:35:48,900 --> 00:35:51,140
I guess Ya convinced him.

602
00:35:51,650 --> 00:35:52,650
In that case,

603
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:55,860
the establishment
of the Inspectorate Office is necessary.

604
00:35:57,940 --> 00:35:58,740
If so,

605
00:35:59,540 --> 00:36:01,060
do you have any objections

606
00:36:01,300 --> 00:36:03,820
to the establishment
of the Inspectorate Office?

607
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:05,860
I have no objection.

608
00:36:08,140 --> 00:36:09,940
Good. It's decided, then.

609
00:36:10,340 --> 00:36:11,340
From today on,

610
00:36:11,380 --> 00:36:13,300
Pingyue is officially in charge
of the Inspectorate Office.

611
00:36:13,380 --> 00:36:14,900
All affairs of the Inspectorate Office

612
00:36:14,900 --> 00:36:16,340
can be reported directly to me.

613
00:36:16,660 --> 00:36:17,770
No need to report
to the two Chancellors

614
00:36:17,770 --> 00:36:18,300
and Six Ministries.

615
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:19,580
Pingyue,

616
00:36:20,140 --> 00:36:21,580
you can handpick the internal staff

617
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:23,580
for the Inspectorate Office.

618
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:26,380
Allocating
Mingsheng Military Drill Ground

619
00:36:27,060 --> 00:36:28,580
