628
00:36:51,860 --> 00:36:53,940
The Ministry of Revenue collects
tens of millions of taels of tax

629
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:55,140
every year.

630
00:36:55,220 --> 00:36:57,220
Now you can't even spare 30,000 taels?

631
00:36:57,860 --> 00:36:59,220
