632
00:37:03,340 --> 00:37:04,060
Pingyue,

633
00:37:05,580 --> 00:37:08,900
I've established
the Inspectorate Office for you.

634
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:13,060
You have to share my burden
in the future.

635
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:14,580
Yes, Father.

636
00:37:16,380 --> 00:37:17,340
Well.

637
00:37:19,140 --> 00:37:21,900
The Qin Family's case and the military
provisions and funds case...

638
00:37:22,140 --> 00:37:23,580
These two cases

639
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:26,060
