to the Inspectorate Office.

640
00:37:26,580 --> 00:37:28,860
Now that the Inspectorate Office
has been established,

641
00:37:28,860 --> 00:37:30,380
I'll find an assistant for you.

642
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:31,300
Assistant?

643
00:37:31,660 --> 00:37:33,660
With so much power in your hands,

644
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:35,780
you'll need someone to assist you.

645
00:37:37,740 --> 00:37:40,060
I'll choose Su Family's Young Master,
Su Ronghua.

646
00:37:43,220 --> 00:37:45,620
Su Ronghua was Prince Su's teacher

647
00:37:45,860 --> 00:37:47,060
and he is a member
of the noble families.

648
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:48,900
He'll definitely keep a close eye
on Her Highness.

649
00:37:49,300 --> 00:37:50,900
Putting in someone from the Su Family

650
00:37:51,220 --> 00:37:53,060
is a way to appease the noble families.

651
00:37:53,940 --> 00:37:54,780
It's decided then.

652
00:37:55,140 --> 00:37:56,540
Have the Secretariat prepare a decree.

653
00:37:57,180 --> 00:37:58,700
Pingyue, pick a date

654
00:37:58,820 --> 00:38:01,340
to establish the Inspectorate Office
as soon as possible.

655
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,180
Yes, Father.

656
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:08,620
I'm afraid Father has developed
a distrust of us.

657
00:38:09,170 --> 00:38:11,520
[Mingyue Palace]

658
00:38:14,140 --> 00:38:14,900
Sir.

659
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:19,060
If the ruler is not upright,
what should the ministers do?

660
00:38:21,380 --> 00:38:24,060
The ministers should admonish him
with their lives.

661
00:38:25,060 --> 00:38:27,380
And if the ruler doesn't accept it,
what then?

662
00:38:28,900 --> 00:38:30,060
As those in front fall,
those behind take up their positions.

663
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:31,300
What if it still won't work?

664
00:38:32,140 --> 00:38:33,140
If that's the case,

665
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:36,140
choose another wise ruler.

666
00:38:37,690 --> 00:38:39,900
All right, that's all for today.

667
00:38:41,220 --> 00:38:43,460
Mr. Su, thank you for the lesson today.

668
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:46,540
Your Highness.

669
00:38:47,140 --> 00:38:49,820
Come on, bow to Mr. Su.

670
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:54,940
Your Highness.

671
00:38:56,540 --> 00:38:59,140
I accept this honor on one condition.

672
00:39:00,580 --> 00:39:02,980
I wonder what you can offer me.

673
00:39:04,900 --> 00:39:07,180
What do you want?

674
00:39:09,860 --> 00:39:11,100
But Your Highness

675
00:39:11,730 --> 00:39:14,850
and Prince Su may not agree
to my condition.

676
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:19,860
Just tell us.

677
00:39:21,940 --> 00:39:23,140
From now on...

678
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,940
