00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:45,940
It's in my mansion.

681
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:47,660
Uncle, you don't need to be so formal.

682
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:49,740
Please sit down.

683
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:51,100
Thank you, Your Highness.

684
00:40:01,660 --> 00:40:04,980
Your Highness, there are so many things
in the Shangguan Family

685
00:40:06,220 --> 00:40:08,460
that I can't handle them all.

686
00:40:09,020 --> 00:40:10,380
Now that a mistake has been made,

687
00:40:11,620 --> 00:40:15,100
I'm here to ask you

688
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:18,980
to close the Qin Family's cases.

689
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:28,060
Now, the Qin Family is involved
in two cases,

690
00:40:29,140 --> 00:40:30,100
the military provisions and funds case

691
00:40:30,940 --> 00:40:32,100
and the case of framing.

692
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:36,620
How much do you know
about these two cases?

693
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:43,940
Your Highness,

694
00:40:44,300 --> 00:40:46,740
my father didn't know anything
about them.

695
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:48,100
To be honest, Your Highness,

696
00:40:48,300 --> 00:40:50,580
the Qin Family's case was already
a case with solid evidence

697
00:40:50,580 --> 00:40:52,620
when it came to my father's attention.

698
00:40:53,140 --> 00:40:54,500
Despite his selfish motives,

699
00:40:54,580 --> 00:40:56,660
he's not a man who can't distinguish
between right and wrong.

700
00:40:57,100 --> 00:40:58,220
What's going on then?

701
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:00,620
His Majesty takes sides with Mr. Xiao

702
00:41:00,860 --> 00:41:02,500
in the fight for military power
in the Northwest.

703
00:41:02,700 --> 00:41:04,580
My father was afraid that His Majesty
would hear and believe slanders,

704
00:41:04,660 --> 00:41:06,460
so he sent someone
to investigate the Qin Family.

705
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:09,380
My father's intention was
to rectify any mistakes

706
00:41:09,580 --> 00:41:11,100
and let them go
if there were no mistakes.

707
00:41:12,980 --> 00:41:13,740
And then what happened?

708
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:15,300
But the word then became

709
00:41:15,420 --> 00:41:17,460
finding out the Qin Family's fault.

710
00:41:18,020 --> 00:41:19,940
The Ministry of War found nothing
after the investigation.

711
00:41:19,940 --> 00:41:22,740
So they tore up the Military Record
and submitted it to the Censorate

712
00:41:22,740 --> 00:41:23,940
for reporting
on the fulfillment of their duties.

713
00:41:24,100 --> 00:41:25,020
The Censorate

714
00:41:25,020 --> 00:41:27,300
saw that Yang Quan was a traitor.

715
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:30,260
The Qin Family was working
under him at that time.

716
00:41:30,660 --> 00:41:31,660
In the battle to defend the city,
our soldiers and enemies

717
00:41:31,660 --> 00:41:34,180
were in equal numbers,
yet we lost the war.

718
00:41:34,700 --> 00:41:37,380
It was very strange.

719
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:38,580
Hence,

720
00:41:39,460 --> 00:41:42,180
the Censorate made evidence
out of nothing

721
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:44,260
and made Luo Juan a witness.

722
00:41:46,420 --> 00:41:48,300
In fact, even if the Ministry of Justice
had got Luo Juan's testimony,

723
00:41:48,420 --> 00:41:50,180
it would not have been enough
to convict the Qin Family.

724
00:41:50,940 --> 00:41:52,020
But the Ministry of Justice thought

725
00:41:52,020 --> 00:41:53,780
that my father wanted
to thoroughly investigate the Qin Family

726
00:41:54,140 --> 00:41:56,900
and the Qin Family seemed
to have deserved it.

727
00:41:57,100 --> 00:41:59,140
So the Ministry of Justice
added another piece of evidence.

728
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:00,220
During the search,

729
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:02,580
the taels of gold and forged letters
were planted in the Qin's Mansion

730
00:42:02,740 --> 00:42:04,260
to form a complete evidence and clues

731
00:42:04,580 --> 00:42:06,420
together with Luo Juan's testimony.

732
00:42:10,380 --> 00:42:11,660
And Uncle, you felt

733
00:42:12,460 --> 00:42:13,780
that Father had gone too far this time,

734
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:15,780
so you wanted to give Father a warning

735
00:42:16,660 --> 00:42:19,700
and decided to go ahead
with this big case.

736
00:42:21,220 --> 00:42:22,740
When I started looking into it,

737
00:42:23,860 --> 00:42:25,060
they started panicking,

738
00:42:25,180 --> 00:42:27,180
trying desperately
to cover up their guilt.

739
00:42:27,660 --> 00:42:28,860
And Uncle, you thought

740
00:42:29,420 --> 00:42:30,580
I was being used

741
00:42:31,020 --> 00:42:32,100
and deceived,

742
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,020
right?

