00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:35,580
Now that things have come to this,

744
00:42:36,660 --> 00:42:38,580
I don't want to argue any further.

745
00:42:39,900 --> 00:42:43,100
I just hope that you can stop here

746
00:42:43,180 --> 00:42:45,060
and discontinue the stalemate.

747
00:42:48,180 --> 00:42:50,580
I understand your determination.

748
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,740
But the Shangguan Family

749
00:42:53,940 --> 00:42:55,940
is the foundation of you
and the Crown Prince.

